      <abstract>The California Avenue Congregational Church was first gathered in 1883 and the
        church building was constructed in 1887. The church federated with the Monroe Street Church
        of Christ to form the Monroe Street Federated Church in 1918. The church dissolved in 1933.
        This collection primarily contains administrative and membership related records and
        includes vital membership records, church meeting minutes, a newsletter, and
        directory.</abstract>
